PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Jennifer Marie HAMMERLUND, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 156901
COA: 333827 Supreme Court of Michigan. October 11, 2018

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the motion of plaintiff-appellee to extend the time for filing its supplemental brief is GRANTED. The supplemental brief submitted on October 9, 2018, is accepted as timely filed.
